A Robot needs to find how far it must travel between two points on a 2D-plane .develop a c-program to calculate the straight line distance between the given coordinates
  the program goes-----
  #include<stdio.h>
#include<math.h>
void main()
{
    float x1,y1,x2,y2,distance;
    printf("enter the first coordinates");
    scanf("%f %f" ,&x1,&y1);
    printf("enter the second coordinates");
    scanf("%f %f",&x2,&y2);
    distance= sqrt(pow((x2-x1),2)+pow((y2-y1),2));
    printf("the distance is %f,distance");
}
the output-----
  enter the first coordinates2
3
enter the second coordinates1
2
the distance is 0.000000,distance
